   <description>
      <short>
         <en>Gapp essentials is a mandatory plugin to enable extended functionalities on Gapp, a GLPI mobile app.</en>
      </short>
      <long>
         <en>Gapp Essentials is a mandatory plugin that enables advanced functionality in Gapp, the mobile application for GLPI. Beginning with Gapp 2, the Gapp Essentials plugin has become a prerequisite for the app's operation. We strongly recommend updating GLPI to safeguard against security vulnerabilities. The versions currently supported are: -10.0.3+ Currently enables: -Access to ticket documents -Plugins list to Self-service users -Max. uploadable file size -Allowed filetypes -Download file size</en>
      </long>
   </description>
